title: WiFi Range Extender
description: Stronger and Fast WiFi Signal. 4 High-gain antennas and advance central processor to better extend wireless signal to hard-to-reach areas - Coverage up to 3280 Square feet and connects up to 35 devices - delivers ultra-stable bandwidth for online gaming, video chat and even streaming 4K HD video

title: Linksys AC750
description: Eliminate dead zones and boost Wi-Fi Boost Wi-Fi range for better coverage and signal strength with the Linksys AC750 Wi-Fi Range Extender (RE6250). The AC750 Range Extender extends your existing Wi-Fi range, so you can enjoy a stronger Wi-Fi signal in every room of your house - and even outdoors. Works with any Wi-Fi router The AC750 Range Extender is compatible with all Wi-Fi routers, including your existing unit or those from service providers. Easily expand Wi-Fi without the need to modify any of your router's settings. Fast transfer speeds with dual-band Wi-Fi Enjoy uninterrupted streaming, smooth online gaming, and more thanks to this range extender's simultaneous wireless dual bands.

title: Google Nest Wifi 2 Pack
description: Nest Wi-Fi blankets your whole home in reliable coverage. It works behind the scenes to keep your Wi-Fi fast and buffering at bay. Nest Wi-Fi is easy to set up in the Google Home app. Then connect and manage devices in your network. Plus pause Wi-Fi to limit screen time for the kids. Automatic updates help your network stay safe and sound. And when you need some extra help, just ask Google in your Nest Wi-Fi point. Use your voice to control connected devices, play your favorite music, broadcast messages around the house, and more. Nest Wi-Fi manages your whole connected home. One Wi-Fi router with one Wi-Fi point is strong enough to handle up to 200 connected devices, and fast enough to stream multiple 4K videos at a time. This is Wi-Fi the way it should be.

title: NETGEAR AX2400
description: Upgrade to true high-performance WiFi with the NETGEAR Nighthawk AX2400 WiFi 6 Router (RAX29). It delivers blazing-fast Internet speeds and reliable connectivity to every device in your network, allowing you to stream picture-perfect 4K UHD content to smart TVs, mobile devices, and gaming consoles with up to 2.4Gbps wireless speeds. WiFi 6 technology gives you access to the latest WiFi technology with up to 4X more WiFi capacity. Its three high-powered antennas will extend your wireless range for maximum coverage throughout your home so you can enjoy WiFi wherever you are.

title: Andoer 4G LTE
description: Support 802.11b/g/n network protocol, the transmission rate up to 300Mbps. Equipped with 4 high-gain antennas, which can cover a larger area and ensure stable signal transmission. Apart from an Ethernet connection, X10 faciliates wireless communication through 4G LTE or WiFi networks and builds a secure network for loT systems like smart control of power supplies. Equipped with SIM card slot, support Nano SIM card. 4G network can be used to cover an entire home, no network cable required.
